  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they say, this room is now being closed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You are the last one to see, because the Prime Minister of Spain is a Socialist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time it was Gonzales.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even if they have a king, they-- they need to have-- but now, he lost the election just recently.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was interesting to talk to the officers on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were telling about how the railroads were blown up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were no use to the German railroad cars, because the German railroad cars are of European width, while the railroad-- there are only two countries in Europe that have a wide-gauge railroad.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that would be Soviet Union and Spain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in Spain, I also had to get off the French train and walk to the Spanish train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, the Germans couldn't do that, so they had lot of delays trying to get the gauge for their train to roll.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were complaining already at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In 1941, they were complaining about the partisans that were quite active, attacking [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] any stray German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they did hang a lot of people, but they were not-- they-- they said that they didn't know anything about the atrocities.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because I listened to BBC, I knew that there were some atrocities and they would deny that completely.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I know in our German school we didn't know about that either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, you know, it was kept strictly secret about the atrocities that they have committed, putting people in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't see any concentration camps when I was traveling through Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The train went through Breslau and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I-- I didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing is that in France, the water was not safe.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
